      ECHO OTHERS %N turns %a and the blade's inherent radiance begins to intensify.
      ECHO PLAYER You turn Weapon Breaker, which begins to glow brighter.
      EQUAL ITEMVAL4 89
      EQUAL ITEMVAL5 300
      IFVAR ITEMBIT1 = 1
        DAMAGEPLR BODYONLY 300 The glow hurts your eyes and, this time, your body as well.
      ENDIF
      IFVAR ITEMBIT1 = 0
        IFVAR ITEMBIT0 = 1
