      ECHO PLAYER You push on a small rod embedded into the side of the naginata and extend the glimmering albescent blade.
      ECHO OTHERS %N slides %h hand along the pole of %h naginata and a glimmering albescent blade snaps into place.
      EQUAL ITEMVAL3 9
      EQUAL ITEMVAL1 1
      EQUAL ITEMADJ3 1130
    ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER The albescent blade is already extended.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB PULL -1
    CLEARVERB
    IFVAR ITEMVAL1 ! 2
      ECHO PLAYER You pull your hand back along the shaft of your naginata and pull the small rod back into place. A dark shadowsteel blade snaps into place, its tip cruelly barbed.
      ECHO OTHERS %N slides %h hand along the shaft of %h naginata and a dark shadowsteel blade springs into place, its barbed tip glistening.
      EQUAL ITEMVAL3 8
      EQUAL ITEMVAL1 2
      EQUAL ITEMADJ3 643
