PUNCTURE_WEAPON
WEIGHT 7
VOLUME 3
PARAMETER1 12
SUBSTANCE HARDMETAL
CRAFTABLE
ENCRUSTABLE
IFPREVERB LOOK -1
  IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER ----%cItembit6 = 1 makes this a poison papenheimer (ex-1834), tap to coat w/Poison 25, 3 uses per day, uses ITEMVAL1
    ECHO PLAYER Itembit7 = 1 makes this Cammora's papenheimer (ex-1849), conc for mass protection w/10 uses per day, uses ITEMVAL1%c----
  ENDIF
  IFVAR ITEMBIT7 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER The rare and beautiful metal known as sparkling diamontine has been crafted
    ECHO PLAYER with incredible care and agility into this supple blade. Not even the tiniest
    ECHO PLAYER inconsistancy mars the surface of the weapon, the glowing pinpoints of light
    ECHO PLAYER within radiating their radiance unimpeded. The hilt is formed from a single
    ECHO PLAYER chunk of the unprocessed ore, showing that even in its unfinished and rough
    ECHO PLAYER state the beauty of the rock cannot be hidden.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR ITEMBIT6 = 1
  IFPREVERB TAP -1
    CLEARVERB
    EQUAL dummy1 ITEMVAL1
    MOD dummy1 100
    IFVAR dummy1 ! DATE
      EQUAL ITEMVAL1 DATE
    ENDIF
    IFVAR ITEMVAL4 ! 0
      ECHO PLAYER Nothing happens. Perhaps you should try again later.
      ECHO OTHERS %N taps %a.
    ENDIF
    IFVAR ITEMVAL4 = 0
      IFVAR ITEMVAL1 < 300
        ECHO PLAYER As you tap the hilt, poison springs from a hidden reservoir and flows down the blade.
        ECHO OTHERS As %N taps the hilt of %a, poison springs from a hidden reservoir and flows down the blade.
        EQUAL ITEMVAL4 75
        EQUAL ITEMVAL5 8
        ADD ITEMVAL1 100
      ELSE
        ECHO PLAYER Nothing happens. Perhaps you should try again later.
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR ITEMBIT7 = 1
  IFPREVERB CONCENTRATE -1
    CLEARVERB
    EQUAL dummy1 ITEMVAL1
    MOD dummy1 100
    IFVAR dummy1 ! DATE
      EQUAL ITEMVAL1 DATE
    ENDIF
    IFVAR ITEMVAL1 < 1000
      ECHO PLAYER You concentrate intently on the sparkles within the diamontine and within moments some of those sparkles seem to leave the blade and coat the air around you.
      ECHO OTHERS %N concentrates intently on %h paperheimer. Suddenly, some of the tiny sparkles within the blade itself seem to seperate from the weapon to surround her form.
      SPELL 130 50
      ADD ITEMVAL1 100
    ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER You begin to focus upon %a but realize that its power is spent for the day.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB WAVE -1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You wave your papenheimer through a dizzying array of motions, a trail of sparkling light following in its wake.
    ECHO OTHERS A sparkling trail of light follows the path of %N's papenheimer as she waves it through a series of complex patterns.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
;
; I# 502 : Claidhmore
INUMBER 502
NAME 444
TWOHAND_WEAPON
WEIGHT 26
VOLUME 7
PARAMETER1 28
SUBSTANCE HARDMETAL
CRAFTABLE
ENCRUSTABLE
IFPREVERB LOOK -1
  IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER ----%cItembit6 = 1 makes this Tain's Claidhmore (ex-1846) Tap/Thump/Rub it to activate powers.%c----
  ENDIF
  IFVAR ITEMBIT6 = 1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER Exhaustive labor has gone in to the forming of this blade. Everything from
    ECHO PLAYER its piercing tip, to it intricately adorned hilt bespeaks power. A flawless
    ECHO PLAYER diamond, a star sapphire and a beautiful emerald have been placed with care
    ECHO PLAYER into the grip itself, lending their beauty to the construct.
    IFVAR ITEMVAL3 = 5
      ECHO PLAYER The flawless diamond appears to be glowing slightly.
    ENDIF
    IFVAR ITEMVAL3 = 6
      ECHO PLAYER The beautiful emerald appears to be glowing slightly.
    ENDIF
    IFVAR ITEMVAL3 = 7
      ECHO PLAYER The star sapphire appears to be glowing slightly.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR ITEMBIT6 = 1
  IFPREVERB THUMP -1
    IFVAR ITEMVAL3 ! 5
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You touch upon the nearly invisible rune of fire along the blades edge. Flickering tendrils of gold seem to crawl up along the blade, coating its razor sharp edge. The diamond embedded in the hilt glows to life.
      ECHO OTHERS Suddenly thin tendrils of solid gold crawl along the blade of %N's claidhmore, coating its razor edge.
      EQUAL ITEMVAL2 25
      EQUAL ITEMVAL3 5
      EQUAL ITEMVAL5 25
      EQUAL ITEMADJ1 468
      EQUAL ITEMADJ2 470
    ELSE
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You begin to touch the rune of fire and then realize that it is already in that state.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB TAP -1
    IFVAR ITEMVAL3 ! 6
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You touch upon the nearly invisible rune of frost along the blades edge. Flickering tendrils of silver seem to crawl up along the blade, coating its razor sharp edge. The emerald embedded in the hilt glows to life.
      ECHO OTHERS Suddenly thin tendrils of shimmering silver crawl along the blade of %N's claidhmore, coating its razor edge.
      EQUAL ITEMVAL2 25
      EQUAL ITEMVAL3 6
      EQUAL ITEMVAL5 25
      EQUAL ITEMADJ1 292
      EQUAL ITEMADJ2 470
    ELSE
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You begin to touch the rune of frost and then realize that it is already in that state.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB RUB -1
    IFVAR ITEMVAL3 ! 7
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You touch upon the nearly invisible rune of lightning along the blades edge. Flickering tendrils of platinum seem to crawl up along the blade, coating its razor sharp edge. The star sapphire embedded in the hilt glows to life.
      ECHO OTHERS Suddenly thin tendrils of solid platinum crawl along the blade of %N's claidhmore, coating its razor edge.
      EQUAL ITEMVAL2 25
      EQUAL ITEMVAL3 7
      EQUAL ITEMVAL5 25
      EQUAL ITEMADJ1 563
      EQUAL ITEMADJ2 470
    ELSE
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You begin to touch the rune of lightning and then realize that it is already in that state.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
