PARAMETER1 75
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAMINE
This large wooden pole is nearly forty feet in length and three feet
around. Black plastic lengths of wire dangle like snakes from the top
of the pole where they are attached to rusting metal objects. The
metal cones are imbedded firmly in the wood of a cross-bar that is
nailed into the top of the pole.
*DESCRIPTION_END
