;
; I# 987 : Zulfikhar
INUMBER 987
NAME 1135
SLASH_WEAPON
WEIGHT 11
VOLUME 6
PARAMETER1 18
SUBSTANCE HARDMETAL
IFPREVERB LOOK -1
  IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER ----%cThis is a unique auction item created by Montar, Conc/Rub (Globe II, 2 charges)/Push (Invig II, 1 charge), 30 charges/game day%c----
  ENDIF
  ECHO PLAYER Made of finely tempered steel the blade of this weapon extends to the three feet in length at its longest. The blade itself is extremely curved and has a bifurcated, or forked tip. The cutting edges of the blade are barbed, adding to the damage when pulled from a victim. Dancing along the surface of the blade are archaic symbols in a foreign language. The hilt is of polished lapus-lazuli bounde with a comfortable leather cord.
  ECHO OTHERS %N looks at the zulfikhar.
ENDIF
IFVERB CONCENTRATE -1
  ECHO PLAYER The archaic runes shimmer in your mind, exposing their meaning to you....
  ECHO PLAYER "I forge and dedicate this sword to He whose light fills the world, Chakda."
  ECHO PLAYER "The last remnant of Meccrad rests within this sword, created in the ruins that houses the forge of the Master of Steel, Steissar."
  ECHO PLAYER "As long as I hold this weapon will I carry my home with me, even as I lead the tribe on the search for a new blessed land."
  ECHO PLAYER "I, Nuraldim, Sword of the Heavens, pledge the Oath of Kin with this blade and accept the task set before myself and my two brothers. Let the light of Chakda burn brightly for us all."
ENDIF
IFPREVERB RUB -1
  CLEARVERB
  EQUAL dummy1 ITEMVAL1
  MOD dummy1 100
  IFVAR dummy1 ! DATE
    EQUAL ITEMVAL1 DATE
  ENDIF
  IFVAR ITEMVAL1 < 2900
    ECHO PLAYER You feel a surge of power rush through you, forcing you to lift the weapon to the heavens and intone, "For the glory of Chakda and Meccrad!"
    ECHO OTHERS %N raises %h zulfikhar to the heavens and intones, "For the glory of Chakda and Meccrad!", a brilliant light crackles around the sword and then flows down to cover %N.
    SPELL 133 50
    ADD ITEMVAL1 200
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER The sword remains quiescent, obviously re-charging.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
  CLEARVERB
  EQUAL dummy1 ITEMVAL1
  MOD dummy1 100
  IFVAR dummy1 ! DATE
    EQUAL ITEMVAL1 DATE
  ENDIF
  IFVAR ITEMVAL1 < 3000
    ECHO PLAYER Golden light fills the blade of the weapon and then shoots forth in beams to cover your entire body, invigorating tired muscles!
    ECHO OTHERS Golden light fills the blade of %N's zulfikhar, shooting forth to cover %N's entire body!
    SPELL 335 50
    ADD ITEMVAL1 100
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER The sword remains quiescent, obviously re-charging.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
