  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR ITEMBIT6 = 1
  IFPREVERB PULL -1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You pull back on the crackling tendon and an arrow of transluscent force appears on the string, nocked and ready to fire.
    ECHO OTHERS %N pulls back on %h bowstring and a force arrow appears on %h spinebow.
    EQUAL ITEMVAL3 1
    EQUAL ROUNDTIME 2
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB WAVE -1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You wave the twisted spine through the air, filling the area with the stench of death.
    ECHO OTHERS %N waves a twisted spined through the air. Suddenly, you are nearly overwhelmed by the stench of death.
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB RUB -1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER As you rub your hand along the twisted spine, the air around you shimmers into a field of magical protection.
    ECHO OTHERS %N rubs %h hands along the length of a twisted spine.
    ECHO OTHERS Suddenly, the air around %N shimmers into a field of magical protection.
    SPELL 326 30
    SUB MANAPOINTS 5
  ENDIF
ENDIF
