;
; I# 1708 : Staff (critter weapon)
INUMBER 1708
NAME 194
CRUSH_WEAPON
WEIGHT 20
VOLUME 7
PARAMETER1 30
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAMINE
Long tendrils of shadow intertwine forming the entirety of the staff.
The shadows pulse with a malovelence and life that is drawn from the
darkest depths of primeval evil.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFTOUCH -1
 IFVAR RAC ! 9
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER Shadows flow into your mind, crushing your will to resist, you feel your will to live slowly fading away as evil chuckling resonates in your head. Your head clears after what seems like an eternity, but is only a moment, a fading voice speaks in your mind, "Touch not again that which you can not control!"
   ECHO OTHERS %N gasps and holds %h head as %s crumples to the floor, a look of pure terror crossing %h face. After a moment, %N stands again, face pale and body shivering.
   POSITION LAY
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB WIELD -1
  ECHO PLAYER Shadows detach themselves from your surroundings and flow into your staff, enveloping you in their darkness and evil.
  ECHO OTHERS Shadows detach themselves from the surroundings and flow into %N's staff, and then into %i, covering %N in an aura of darkness.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PULL -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR RNUM = 330
    ECHO PLAYER The shadows in the room darken and fill the chamber with a cold darkness as the staff speaks, in your mind, "Shall we feed, Master?"
    ECHO OTHERS %N raises the staff and the shadows in the room respond...The darkness becomes more palatable and you get the sense that the shadows are awaiting %N's command.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR RNUM ! 330
    ECHO PLAYER You call upon the shadows in the area, and they instantly spring to your bidding, filling everyone else with a sense of dread and terror.
    ECHO OTHERS A cold chill washes down your spine as you sense the shadows around you begin to fill with a dark, malovelent power.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB RUB -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You feel your eyes flash a dangerous red.
  ECHO OTHERS %N's eyes flash with a bright redness for a brief moment.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CARESS -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You touch the hungry staff to the corpse and feel a brief surge of power as the darkness from the corpse is sucked into the staff.
  ECHO OTHERS %N touches the staff to the corpse...the staff pulsates strongly as something is ripped from the corpse and flows into the weapon. From somewhere far off, you can hear the scream of a soul in torment....
ENDIF
IFPREVERB KISS -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You bring the staff close to you and whisper words of darkness to it...
  ECHO OTHERS You sense darkness forming behind you, lusting for your light. The feeling is intense...the darkness is behind you...reaching for you...hungering for you...yet, when you glance over your shoulder....you see nothing.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
  CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You gaze hungrily at the pulsing artery of your victims neck, and then in one savage movement sink your fangs into the unresisting flesh, drinking deeply as the salty, crimson liquid gushes down your throat!
   ECHO OTHERS %N hovers over your neck, %h eyes pulsing with a hungry lust. Unable to move you watch helplessly as %N sinks his fangs into your unresisting flesh, you feel your life's blood flowing from your body into the hungry, eager throat of your attacker.
ENDIF
;
; I# 1736 : Bola (Aerion weapon)
INUMBER 1736
NAME 1459
WEIGHT 5
VOLUME 5
SUBSTANCE SOFTMETAL
THROWN_WEAPON
PARAMETER1 5
IFPREVERB LOOK -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The bola consists of three heavy metal balls connected with a long leather thong.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB WIELD -1
  IFVAR SKILL19 > 0
    ECHO PLAYER You begin to spin the bola faster and faster overhead.
    ECHO OTHERS %N begins to spin %h bola rapidly over %h head, producing a whistling noise.
  ELSE
    CLEARVERB
    DAMAGEPLR CRUSH 5 %N attempts to wield a bola and only proceeds in clubbing %iself with it.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
;
; I# 1751 : Battleaxe (Deeplander, one-handed)
INUMBER 1751
NAME 18
SLASH_WEAPON
WEIGHT 13
VOLUME 5
PARAMETER1 15
SUBSTANCE HARDMETAL
ENCRUSTABLE
IFPREVERB LOOK -1
  IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER ----%cItembit6 = 1 makes this a fiery/icy battleaxe (ex-598), turn to switch, only changes ITEMVAL3
    ECHO PLAYER Itembit7 = 1 makes this Aircleaver (ex-598), Conc/Turn/Wield (all when wielded) for powers%c----
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR ITEMBIT6 = 1
  IFPREVERB TURN -1
    CLEARVERB
    IFVAR ITEMVAL3 = 2
      EQUAL ITEMVAL3 3
      EQUAL ITEMADJ1 166
      ECHO PLAYER You turn the end of the shaft of %a, causing its blade to freeze.
      ECHO OTHERS %N turns the end of the shaft of %a, causing ice crystals to form on the blade.
    ELSE
      EQUAL ITEMVAL3 2
      EQUAL ITEMADJ1 125
      ECHO PLAYER You turn the end of the shaft of %a, causing flames to appear around its blade.
      ECHO OTHERS %N turns the end of the shaft of %a, causing flames to appear around its blade momentarily.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR ITEMBIT7 = 1
  IFPREVERB SELL -1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER The battleaxe doesn't seem to want to be sold.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR AXEMOVE = 0
    RANDOM AXEMOVE 1 30 500
  ENDIF
  IFITEM -1 WIELDED
    IFVERB CONCENTRATE -1
      IFVAR TIM ! ITEMVAL1
        ECHO ALL The battleaxe glows softly for a moment.
        EQUAL ITEMBIT0 1
        EQUAL ITEMVAL1 TIM
        ECHO PLAYER Aircleaver seems to twist in your grasp, seeking release.
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
    IFPREVERB TURN -1
      IFVAR ITEMBIT0 = 1
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO ALL %A seems to dance with a life of its own, slashing in all directions!
        DAMAGEALL SLASH 20 %N is slashed by the blade!
        EQUAL ITEMBIT0 0
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
    IFPREVERB WIELD -1
      CLEARVERB
      IFVAR ITEMBIT0 = 1
        IFVAR REGION = 0
          IFVAR TERRAIN < 10
            ECHO PLAYER You swing Aircleaver through the air, opening a gate which you step through!
            ECHO OTHERS %N swings %a through the air, slicing a gate in the air!
            ECHO OTHGROUP %P steps through the gate, which closes.
            MOVEGROUP AXEMOVE
            AFFECT AXEMOVE
            ECHO OTHGROUP %P steps out of nothingness!
          ENDIF
        ENDIF
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB PUSH -1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO ALL %A screams in limitless rage!
  ENDIF
  IFPREVERB WAVE -1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO OTHERS %N waves %a, which screams!
    ECHO PLAYER You wave Aircleaver, which screams!
  ENDIF
ENDIF
